@startuml
title Sueca - Diagrama de Componentes

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "Frontend" {
  [Web Client] as Web
}

package "Backend" {
  [GraphQL API] as GraphQL
  [WebSocket Gateway] as WS

  package "Application Layer" {
    [Command Handler] as CH
    [Room Service] as RS
    [Game Service] as GS
  }

  package "Domain Layer" {
    [Game Aggregate] as Game
    [Room Aggregate] as Room
    [Strategies] as Strat
    [State Machine] as State
    [Event Bus] as Bus
  }

  package "Infrastructure" {
    [Repositories] as Repo
    [Event Store] as Store
  }
}

Web --> GraphQL : HTTP (Query/Mutation)
Web --> WS : WS (Subscribe Events)

GraphQL --> CH : execute(command)
GraphQL --> RS : create/join/start
GraphQL --> GS : game queries (snapshot)

CH --> GS : apply command/use case
GS --> Game : domain operations
RS --> Room : lobby operations

Game --> Strat : rules/bot/scoring
Game --> State : validate phase
Game --> Bus : publish(domain events)

Bus --> WS : notify events
GS --> Repo : load/save state
Bus --> Store : append(event)

@enduml